The latest disappearance and video come as part of a four year custody battle in which a judge ruled the boy must stay in Italy with Rigamonti, where he was born.

Carder launched an unsuccessful appeal against the ruling, and has since used an online petition and a website in order to try and keep her son in the US.

When asked about his therapist by his father, Leo tells YouTube viewers: 'She is stupid, she threatens me to say things as well - bad [things] about my dad. I hate her'.

